definitions.definition: An imagined superior type of human being representing a new stage of human development; an übermensch , an overman .
examples: Nietzsche wrote of the coming of the superman .

definitions.definition: A man of extraordinary or seemingly superhuman powers.

main_definition: ( chiefly philosophy ) An imagined superior type of human being representing a new stage of human development; an übermensch , an overman . [from 1903.]
secondary_definitions: A man of extraordinary or seemingly superhuman powers.
